        "timestamp": "2019-05-05 16:41:49.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nNote: For blueprint updates from this patch to be reflected in default ONAP Dublin install, following are required to be completed\n1) Regenerate dcae bootstrap (blueprints get pre-packaged under this container); version update required (https://git.onap.org/dcaegen2/deployments/tree/k8s-bootstrap-container/pom.xml)\n2) Docker container re-released through LF and validated\n3) OOM charts to be updated to reflect updated bootstrap\n\nPls submit the patch on #1; I will work with LF/OOM team for other two items later this week.\n\nIn  meantime for testing (pair-wise or othercase), PRH can be updated locally in your environment by updating the blueprint locally (inside current version of bootstrap pod) and doing redeploy (similar to steps here - htps://wiki.onap.org/display/DW/Cloudify+Blueprint+validation+under+OOM)",
        "patchset_number": 2
